title: Eugens Bio Cafe Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Organic, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quiet place by the Alnatura bio supermarket. Offers organic Italian food plus burgers, salads, soups, cakes; has vegan cake, ice cream, and even raw food dishes. Has soy milk and almond milk for coffee. Comfortable place.
